  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/kernel\/ioconfigdirectory\/1811186-getkeysubdirectories\ncrawled: 2025-12-11T15:43:37Z\n---\n\n# getKeySubdirectories\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvirtual IOReturn getKeySubdirectories(\n intkey,\n OSIterator *&iterator); \n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n- **key**: type of subdirectory to iterate over\n- **iterator**: on return, set to point to an OSIterator\n\n## Return Value\n\nkIOReturnSuccess if the iterator could be created\n\n## Overview\n\nCreates an iterator over subdirectories of a given type of the directory.\n\n## Miscellaneous\n\n- **getIndexEntry**\n- **getIndexKey**\n- **getIndexType**\n- **getIndexValue**\n- **getKeyType**\n- **getKeyValue**\n- **getSubdirectories**\n- **update**\n\n",
